The paper proposes a new model for the multi-armed bandit problem with fairness constraints, which is a common problem in machine learning and optimization. The paper also proposes a new algorithm to solve this problem. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
